{"tid":1749824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀: 據說有些票站已有工作人員進行分流，安排長者優先投票。","createTime":"2019-11-24T06:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T07:31:14.000Z","uid":167469,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9c355e69164dccad77ccc26b6d36b8ff39ea9e35","tid":1749824,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"早前為好友陳祖光拉票後，隨即趕赴沙田徑口選區為黨友張柏源拉票，此區選情同樣激烈，票站外人頭湧湧，排隊投票的人士當中不乏長者。<br />\n<br />\n其實今晨我到票站投票時，發覺屬年長人士身份證「A、B」字頭的投票櫃台人數較少，但不少長者卻在票站外大排長龍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據說有些票站已有工作人員進行分流，安排長者優先投票。在此建議選管會可靈活處理，安排各區票站輪候的長者優先投票，避免他們久候及日曬雨淋。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\nsource: 葉劉淑儀facebook"},{"pid":"ed2e304e39480fa39780116de38acd7a7c316c31","tid":1749824,"uid":221265,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"公然違法"},{"pid":"6bd4aa8f64ba6a79c45cc4d352f74281b5e4eb37","tid":1749824,"uid":214635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"on9，老大撚哂咩"},{"pid":"7237cf54cc4890438173bf5e1c74639294dd225c","tid":1749824,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/78697835_111546956981052_5926815724700958720_o.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=hf4cFlo7sTUAQny7-TOPw_hq5V0rjBF4WDezgjrWtw6_bKMn7fgHxCFXg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=303199931debfce0d6be44c76a027b30&amp;oe=5E43C3EA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F78697835_111546956981052_5926815724700958720_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ohc%3Dhf4cFlo7sTUAQny7-TOPw_hq5V0rjBF4WDezgjrWtw6_bKMn7fgHxCFXg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D303199931debfce0d6be44c76a027b30%26oe%3D5E43C3EA&h=48a44c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e558672dbdc2056bd463f807894bfe10d2459ce5","tid":1749824,"uid":331251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"002f259792d358136120fcf61d9f2f9b91cda0c6","tid":1749824,"uid":224545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:52:18.000Z","msg":"60歲都係中年"},{"pid":"1fbec83e7e3b2d4257f5f6bf2d9ae94d412cbb1f","tid":1749824,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"上面死圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文字版:<br />\n【澄清 &mdash; 不要輕信謠言!!!】<br />\n傳言：<br />\n網上有好多人話，老人家、傷殘人士可以唔駛排隊「打尖」投票。<br />\n<br />\n事實：<br />\n絕無此事！如果大家曾經投票，應該知道進入投票站後，選民按身份證上的英文字母分流領取選票。今早，很多票站大排長龍，票站外只得一條龍，但站內發票枱選民分布未必平均，票站職員靈活處理，只是為了疏導人流。例如某些英文字母的發票枱無人排隊，職員可按情況到站外請相關選民先入內領票。<br />\n<br />\n至於坐輪椅、傷殘人士等，票站職員會特別處理。<br />\n<br />\n票站外的人龍清得更快，人人得益。而最重要、最重要、最重要的是：所有排隊的選民都一定有票投！<br />\n<br />\n選舉熱線：2891 1001<br />\n選舉網站：<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2F&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=b6df1d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\nsource: 2019區議會選舉facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/election.gov.hk/photos/a.106320907503657/111546953647719/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Felection.gov.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.106320907503657%2F111546953647719%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=0cfed3da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/election.gov.hk/photos/a.106320907503657/111546953647719/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"e49d4c4e00ac747107a502e9c39075f02b54c71d","tid":1749824,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"Fuck"},{"pid":"c664135862f59c6d4d723605a1e887c43a7aa74c","tid":1749824,"uid":55010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9c355e69164dccad77ccc26b6d36b8ff39ea9e35","tid":1749824,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"早前為好友陳祖光拉票後，隨即趕赴沙田徑口選區為黨友張柏源拉票，此區選情同樣激烈，票站外人頭湧湧，排隊投票的人士當中不乏長者。<br />\n<br />\n其實今晨我到票站投票時，發覺屬年長人士身份證「A、B」字頭的投票櫃台人數較少，但不少長者卻在票站外大排長龍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據說有些票站已有工作人員進行分流，安排長者優先投票。在此建議選管會可靈活處理，安排各區票站輪候的長者優先投票，避免他們久候及日曬雨淋。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\nsource: 葉劉淑儀facebook"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:00:25.000Z","msg":"其他人又要日曬雨林，知唔知咩叫選舉公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3472c74e2f593bb3d21cbdc440017e9d80528344","tid":1749824,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"公然俾老人家打尖先"},{"pid":"d0717f6e1800a484c4b638cb50b0eccf371dc9ca","tid":1749824,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"Solomon Yue.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6125c4e7d254755ddca9a57400194618f569040","tid":1749824,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8yRridn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8yRridn.jpg&h=6f42fa0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ibDkF2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ibDkF2.gif&h=e6ef6779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2nesfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2nesfV.jpg&h=31f33479&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5d4db48b034050fe47aeb2620478b6ae3fe4d7